Music Video to my holiday hit “SANTA’S SACK” - this is the end credit song for @merryexmasfilm - I play a rock star named Thurston on a quest to write a Christmas classic! This whole song came from a bit of on set improve with director @jcooney7 . The lyrics just started to write themselves. We refined things with composer @batemanmusic who created the music and arranged the song! 
Clearly this was the most fun I’ve ever had in front of the camera. Now GET JOLLY and watch @merryexmasfilm to listen to the full song - now streaming everywhere! 🎅🏻 🎸

My FALL FILM CAMP is COMING SOON! I’m excited to share my cinema secrets and get you fired up and prepared for your filmmaking journey! 
 
This seminar is a crash course to the industry, geared towards ACTORS, WRITERS and DIRECTORS. The event will include a lecture portion, fun and informative stories from my time on various movie sets, as well as a Q&A, followed by lighting round consultation/pitch sessions with VIPs.

With an introduction by producer David Gere - 
Topics included in the discussion will be:
* Secrets to screenwriting
* Film Fundraising Methods
* How to get distribution
* Becoming Cast-able: Marketing tips for actors
* Advanced Directing Techniques and more! 
It’s all happening 1:00pm, Saturday October 7th at The Greenwich Odeum on Main St. in East Greenwich! 

Pre order your tickets online (LINK IN BIO) or at the box office! 
I hope to see ya there! 🎥❤️
